title: About Me
text: Hi! I am Swapnaja, a current student @ George Mason. In terms of courses,I am enrolled in STAT-515, CS-504, and AIT-580. After working for a few years as a Market Research Analyst, I was intrigued with the field of Decision Sciences and Analytics. Hence, I decided to take up Masters degree at GMU.
